    <briefdescription>
<para>Service for controlling EPS load switches and power rails. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This module provides control over the satellite&apos;s power distribution. It interacts with the GPIOs, Load Switches, and Current Monitors into logical rails.</para>
<para>It is responsible for:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>toggling physical power switches</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>reading voltage and current telemetry</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>implementing software-based overcurrent protection </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
